descriptionHtml:
Become an oil tycoon by managing your wells, production and refining! You'll explore and buy new equipment, erect new buildings and entire factories, build gas stations and set up an infrastructure of shopping malls and hotels near highways.

All for the sake of oil, energy and world domination! Make your opinion count, and build your empire!
